<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
      .header { background-color: #2e3d99; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 20px; }
      .order-details { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
      .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Your Order Has Shipped!</h1>
        <h2>Order #<%= @order.id.to_s.rjust(6, '0') %></h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <%= @order.ship_to_name %>,</p>
        
        <p>Great news! Your order from Aloop Offroad has shipped and is on its way to you.</p>
        
        <div class="order-details">
          <h3>Shipping Details:</h3>
          <p><strong>Ship To:</strong><br>
          <%= @order.ship_to_name %><br>
          <%= @order.address_line_1 %><br>
          <% if @order.address_line_2.present? %>
            <%= @order.address_line_2 %><br>
          <% end %>
          <%= @order.city %>, <%= @order.state %> <%= @order.postal_code %><br>
          <%= @order.country %></p>
          
          <p><strong>Shipping Method:</strong> <%= @order.shipping_method_name || 'Standard' %></p>
          <p><strong>Order Total:</strong> $<%= sprintf('%.2f', @order.final_price) %></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>You should receive your order within the expected delivery timeframe for your selected shipping method. If you have any questions about your order, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for choosing Aloop Offroad!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The Aloop Offroad Team</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Aloop Offroad | sales@aloop.com</p>
        <p>This email was sent regarding your order #<%= @order.id.to_s.rjust(6, '0') %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>